    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2001 BMW M3 in concours-level condition. This E46 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a precision Getrag 420G manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the high-pressure Double VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells for long-term reliability. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with structural plates, ensuring the chassis remains rigid under high lateral load. Finished in its original factory paint with zero oxidation, the car maintains its factory-spec limited-slip differential and M-tuned suspension geometry. This is a turn-key example for the discerning purist seeking a peak analog driving experience.",
